com/v/t64.5771-25/38974571_1014728126426150_3738956639406327634_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UyJSZy4tt-QQ7kNvgFR9WC7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAyprt_FyrxKsvSQI7Zpud6we6lsYzjgKHgZbl2RNk0Sg&oe=67810433"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Trailer_End_Card-Recovered.png", "id": "273391962004750", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974788_273391965338083_1886064065722113930_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Q5A7unxKNfYQ7kNvgH9DRV8&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAz_fYkVNEwxcKrE2X51-mCPJf00Y8Sdb1vnZzcyKvrRQ&oe=67810232"}, "display_name": "Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures", "keywords": ["Cockpit", "Alien", "Green", "Space", "Physics"], "long_description": "Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures is a VR cockpit game combining ship management with action-arcade combat. You play as a (sometimes effective) bounty hunter with possibly questionable morals, currently in possession of a powerful little alien that you may or may not have stolen/liberated from the evil Empire. As the Empire closes in, you'll need to find a way to balance your ship's management with the onslaught of attacks. Do you have what it takes to survive?\n\n\u2022 Become one with the ship: Immerse yourself in a cockpit packed full from ceiling to floor with distinct physics-based interactions (Though make sure to keep your eye on them all if you want to survive!).\n\n\u2022 Rebel against The Empire: Engage in thrilling dogfights as squads of enemies pursue you to re-capture the small green treasure aboard your ship - shoot bullets, launch bombs, and raise your shields. It's going to get bumpy!\n\n\u2022 Navigate the vacuum of space: Control the ship with a radical and easy-to-use virtual flight stick design, dodge your way through hazardous space environments, and don't forget to do a barrel roll!\n\n\u2022 The little guy: Who could forget your cosmic friend, Ziggy?! This mysterious creature is a perfect fuel source. You can also play with them, use them as a resource, feed them, and most importantly pet them!\n\n\u2022 The Journey: Fight your way through 13 unique levels total. Forge a different path each time by beating challenges and unlocking harder worlds en route.", "short_description": "Ziggy's Cosmic Adventures is a VR cockpit game combining ship management with action-arcade combat. You play as a (sometimes effective) bounty hunter with possibly questionable morals, currently in possession of a powerful little alien that you may or may not have stolen/liberated from the evil Empire. As the Empire closes in, you'll need to find a way to balance your ship's management with the onslaught of attacks. Do you have what it takes to survive?"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Ziggy_Monoscopic.png", "id": "1296582511245835", "image_type": "APP_IMG_CUBEMAP_SOURCE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974446_1296582517912501_8438674573824683709_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=q2CgeWKzn3UQ7kNvgGmZ9Jz&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCi8TPZUbDx0UV6tALbS0QId5veRY4n6nrxHOXXVK3yiw&oe=6780F993"}, {"file_name": "CoverSquare.png", "id": "1124369782419830", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036658_1124369785753163_6062844584904789074_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=i6O68wFh09QQ7kNvgE5UE6C&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDCV2BdMW2xcegTMa3cb2EOwrWa-MAXhpLsPdnlvr-NOw&oe=6780F5AF"}, {"file_name": "Icon_v1.png", "id": "1106448921139578", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001696_1106448927806244_1890053882317213161_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KRDntqRJl6gQ7kNvgFaRzmA&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCXSMjxRcCvJpd4g_chie_Rfld0MxvFQYzr9YULEzJ39A&oe=67810162"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "97342